behavior __goal__():
    body:
        bind dishwasher: item where:
            is_dishwasher(dishwasher)
        # Select a dishwasher
        bind soap: item where:
            is_soap(soap) and grabbable(soap)
        # Select dish soap that is grabbable
        achieve close_char(char, dishwasher)
        # Approach the dishwasher to put the dish soap in
        achieve close_char(char, soap)
        # Approach the soap to put it in the dishwasher
        achieve inside(soap, dishwasher)
        # Place the dish soap inside the dishwasher

['1. Locate the dishwasher.', '2. Put dish soap in the dishwasher.', '3. Place the bowls and plates 
into the dishwasher.', '4. Start the dishwasher to wash the bowls and plates.']

behavior __goal__():
    body:
        foreach dishwasher: item:
            if is_dishwasher(dishwasher) and not visited(dishwasher):
                observe(dishwasher, "Locate the dishwasher")
